your friends for some fun and excitement!

{pageend:There are three kinds of battles.}
Single Battle is for two Trainers with one
{pageend:Pokémon each.}
Double Battle is for two Trainers with two
{pageend:Pokémon each.}
Multi Battle is for four Trainers with one Pokémon
each. They battle against each other in teams
of two.

